query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.favorite_count >= 1 AND q.favorite_count <= 10
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('tex')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('color',
'cross-referencing',
'diagrams',
'errors',
'floats',
'formatting',
'header-footer',
'hyperref',
'lists',
'numbering',
'pdftex',
'symbols',
'xetex');
